    "body": "Apparently there is no (easy) way to fix that. The minimum time is the time needed for bootstrap to show the dialog and trigger the `bs.model.shown` event. We could try to bind an action to `00+Enter` (restart without confirm), would need some refactor of keyboard shortcut again so that 00,Enter does not shadow  00 itself. \n"
